editors-announce-2024-uk-tour-buy-tickets-3557188">昨天（3 月 3 日）结束的 Editors 2024 年英国巡演之后举行的</a>，他们将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-announce-2024-uk-shows-including-brixton-academy-dates-buy-tickets-3596362">The Black Keys</a>一起成为今年首批在重新开放的空间演出的艺人之一。</p><p>该场馆因<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/artists/asake">浅酒</a>音乐会上发生悲惨事件而关闭后，于今天<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-announces-reopening-details-with-first-gig-3596293">宣布重新开放</a>。这次碾压导致<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tributes-paid-to-selfless-security-worker-killed-in-brixton-academy-asake-gig-crush-3370071">23 岁的加布里埃尔·哈钦森 (Gabrielle Hutchinson)</a>和<a style="font-family: Verdana, BlinkMacSystemFont, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/woman-injured-during-asakes-o2-academy-brixton-show-dies-due-to-injuries-3368308">33 岁的丽贝卡·伊库梅洛 (Rebecca Ikumelo)</a>死亡。第三人情况危急。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-o2-academy-has-licence-suspended-for-three-months-after-fatal-crowd-crush-3381455">兰贝斯市议会吊销了该场馆的执照</a>后，这座标志性音乐场馆的未来在几个月内仍然充满不确定性，据报道，大都会警察局<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/o2-academy-brixton-faces-indefinite-closure-following-fatal-crowd-crush-3435471">敦促该场馆永久关闭</a>。</p><p> 2023 年 12 月，宣布<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-allowed-to-retain-license-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">如果能够满足“严格”的安全规则，该场馆将被允许保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。</p><p>首场演出将于四月开始，首先是两场致敬演出。</p><p> Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）和 The Smyths（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">The Smiths</a>致敬）将于 4 月 19 日星期五在场馆演出，随后的周五，Definitemightbe（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a>致敬）和 UK Foo Fighters（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>致敬） 4 月 26 日。本周五（3 月 8 日）上午 9 点（格林威治标准时间）演出门票从<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/o2-academy-brixton-tickets-london/venue/507981?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WVMWLAT55xyPTjiVXp0rVUKSUkH3PuSZnRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>开始发售。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/editors-announce-huge-show-at-londons-re-opened-brixton-academy-buy-tickets-3596360">编辑宣布伦敦重新开放的布里克斯顿学院举办大型演出的帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
