dby="caption-attachment-3370627" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3370627" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1.jpg" alt="布里克斯顿学院" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/brixton-academy-asake-getty-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3370627" class="wp-caption-text">在2022年12月15日在Asake演出的人群中，警察录像带布里克斯顿（O2 Academy Brixton）在布里克斯顿（Brixton）。</figcaption></figure><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/petition-launched-to-save-brixton-academy-3436989">发起了一份在线请愿书</a>来抵消关闭， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/artists-and-industry-speak-out-to-save-brixton-academy-itd-be-a-tragedy-to-lose-such-an-iconic-venue-3437059">各种艺术家和行业专业人士也反对可能关闭场地的可能性</a>。</p><p> 2023年12月，宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brixton-academy-allowed-to-retain-license-and-re-open-if-it-can-meet-robust-safety-rules-3498784">如果可以符合“强大的”安全规则，将允许该场地保留其许可证并重新开放</a>。这样做之后，今天早上分享了第一轮复出演出。</p><p> Nirvana UK（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a>致敬）和Smyths（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯</a>致敬）将于4月19日星期五在会场演出，随后肯定会在下一个星期五的星期五（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> ）和UK FOO Fighters（向<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">Foo Fighters</a>致敬） （4 月 26 日）。</p><p>除此之外，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/editors">编辑们</a>还宣布将于 5 月 2 日星期四在伦敦标志性场地举办一场演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-black-keys-announce-2024-uk-shows-including-brixton-academy-dates-buy-tickets-3596362">Black Keys帖子宣布2024英国的演出 - 包括布里克斯顿学院的约会，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
